data.description: Beautiful West Facing  Home Home in a great community Villages at Willow Bay! Backs to Heritage High School and is minutes away from the PGA , Stonebriar Mall, and The Frisco Star!    $30,000 + of updates including new carpet, paint and luxury flooring! Open concept floor plan! 5 bedrooms, 4 full baths, 3 living areas -Living, Media room (includes Media Room Equipment) and Game room over looking the Heritage Ball Park! Primary Bedroom is oversized and has wall of windows.  Secondary bedroom on first floor with full bath and 3 more bedrooms upstairs.  This is a very well designed plan that is sure to exceed your needs. Large oversized utility room with extra shelving for storage and for space for freezer.   3 houses away from the  community pools and walking trails greenbelt.
